'''Tampere urban area''' ({{lang-fi|Tampereen keskustaajama}}, {{lang-sv|Tammerfors centraltätort}}), is the second largest [[urban area]], [[Urban areas in Finland|''taajama'']], in the [[Pirkanmaa]] region, [[Finland]]. It had almost 320.000 inhibitants and 265,86 km² area in 2012. 

